room_title: Escape room "Lock Me If You Can" by EscapeXperience Escape Room in Dallas-Fort Worth
room_description: Locked in a maximum security prison awaiting your execution. You were framed by a serial killer and now facing charges for a murder. There were multiple attempts to escape from this prison. Many people failed and most inmates were recaptured or disappeared without a trace. The guards are on break and you have  to test your luck on escaping from the premises and free yourself including inmates before the prison guards return.Fight the clock to claim your freedom.
